      "text": [
        "اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْ لِي مَا وَأَيْتُ مِنْ نَفْسِي، وَلَمْ تَجِدْ لَهُ وَفَاءً عِنْدي."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "My Allah forgive me what I had promised to myself but Thou didst not find its fulfilment with me."
        ]
      }
    }
